{"tid":1466642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔好再互屌]813機場檢討集中討論","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:50:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:47:58.000Z","uid":139605,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"f4ed7da539f5c9343c5a7f0aa8bef13fb37235ce","tid":1466642,"uid":139605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:50:25.000Z","msg":"屌撚左幾個鐘啦 係時候停一停<br />\n認真諗下一步點行<br />\n<br />\n我拋人地舊磚: 立軍條<br />\n係連登有左共識先<br />\n第時出到去有人違反 <br />\n就可以有理有據咁禁住佢 <br />\n(並不等於捉鬼) 淨係阻止佢等佢冷靜<br />\n冷靜唔到/堅持要做/開始失控先懷疑係鬼<br />\n可以影大頭 搜身攞身份證我覺得就酌情啦 前線決定 但唔建議打人<br />\n影完就護送佢離開(等佢唔好再翻嚟搞事)"},{"pid":"a9a575901556fc70c6a4e8bc1f88ecb906c08695","tid":1466642,"uid":95487,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:50:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有<br />\n唔會捉得晒<br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee82227571aadf5bd065f83bb355e8267712dcce","tid":1466642,"uid":5812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:52:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>聽日一定要做！！！！<br />\n<br />\n理撚得佢有冇鬼！！！！<br />\n<br />\n讓條路俾旅客，然後禮貌鞠躬道歉！！！！<br />\n<br />\n今晚大家早d翻去，準備文宣！！！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"6bb175edb767d9d72225ccb76efd52396a81206a","tid":1466642,"uid":139605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:52:26.000Z","msg":"文宣方向<br />\n1. 721 811唔洗講<br />\n2. 荃灣斬人<br />\n3. 警犬專捉女人 舉真槍<br />\n4. 黑警黑社會公安勾結<br />\n5. 臥底帶頭衝擊警犬"},{"pid":"181749e531b2519172dabd651ed54633ebc6b0bf","tid":1466642,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:52:34.000Z","msg":"下次有鬼唔好郁手 即刻綁住佢問佢野起佢底<br />\n起完掉垃圾桶比記者影 影完再推去廁所自己玩啦"},{"pid":"5feff81e7d7a0fa6cee293e1f97b1bcba0da764c","tid":1466642,"uid":85799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:52:48.000Z","msg":"長期抗爭<br />\n檢討後再出發<br />\n不分化 不割蓆"},{"pid":"7bbaa51d5bfc59adc5d7f548e94c0bfae79b659e","tid":1466642,"uid":32505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:52:48.000Z","msg":"諗下今日失敗既原因係咩先<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係因為唔夠人呀 太少人先俾班鬼帶到風向<br />\n鬼係捉唔哂 夠多人 夠冷靜 點會俾班鬼帶到風向</span></span><br />\n冇去既人自己反省下 唔好賴手足<br />\n<br />\n鬼還鬼 核彈都唔割"},{"pid":"4a911b0ef02b2d8afafccbb2210f8b59950b7f02","tid":1466642,"uid":157436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:53:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5DXohFC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5DXohFC.jpg&h=360ed037&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家請再睇多次"},{"pid":"eaea3f357e1460e68e26c17c920dde3f455b5ab8","tid":1466642,"uid":14274,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:53:38.000Z","msg":"七警都5年前都識暗角先打<br />\n有鏡頭前絕對唔可以行私刑<br />\n<br />\n實有鬼煽動，大家散開又玩，拉住佢又玩，絕對唔好聽佢點"},{"pid":"8c6999ac2f793bf6b3bb5d800b97c3b61a401720","tid":1466642,"uid":20256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:53:39.000Z","m